        <p>Annual descaling overdue (3 years past schedule), boiler heating element burnout secondary to scale buildup. Heavy descaling service plus element replacement. Documented annual descaling protocol with the dining services manager going forward. Total: $1,400. The deferred maintenance pattern (3-year skip) is exactly the cost trap we warn operators about.</p>
