        <h3>Hospital cafeteria, Pasadena. Vulcan VS-6 (6-pan capacity), 6 years old.</h3>
        <p>Water inlet valve plus steam trap replacement. Paired failure: water inlet restricting flow caused steam trap to fail from incomplete drain over 18 months. Replaced both, descaled the boiler while access was open. Total: $720.</p>
