      <div class="story-card">
        <h3>Catering kitchen, Beverly Hills. AccuTemp Steam'N'Hold (boilerless premium), 4 years old.</h3>
        <p>Control panel temperature probe failure. Replaced probe, recalibrated. Total: $640. Note the boilerless design means no scale issues at year 4 (or any year), which is the AccuTemp Steam'N'Hold value proposition for high-volume operations that don't want annual descaling.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="story-card">
        <h3>Hotel banquet kitchen, Long Beach. Market Forge pressure steamer, 9 years old.</h3>
        <p>Pressure relief valve annual safety test failed (couldn't hold pressure spec) plus door gasket replacement. Replaced relief valve with OEM Market Forge part, replaced pressure-rated door gasket. Documented safety inspection for hotel insurance file. Total: $890.</p>
